753
01:11:19,833 --> 01:11:24,082
She started to spend her nights
making pompoms

754
01:11:24,083 --> 01:11:27,624
and eating two-minute noodles.

755
01:12:30,541 --> 01:12:33,999
Each day, with strength and shame,

756
01:12:34,041 --> 01:12:38,249
Mary trudged to the letterbox in hope,

757
01:12:38,250 --> 01:12:43,499
