759
01:13:39,541 --> 01:13:42,957
by the time you read this,
I will be on a plane to New Zealand

760
01:13:42,958 --> 01:13:45,290
to begin a new life.

761
01:13:45,333 --> 01:13:49,415
You probably haven't even noticed
I'd packed my bags.

762
01:13:49,416 --> 01:13:54,040
I have fallen in love
with my penfriend, Desmond,

763
01:13:54,041 --> 01:13:56,707
and I'm going to live
on his sheep farm.

764
01:13:59,166 --> 01:14:02,832
It's been hard to watch you become
a remnant of the person I once loved.

765
01:14:02,833 --> 01:14:05,749
Your research into m-m-mental illness
has been admirable

766
01:14:05,750 --> 01:14:11,040
but your i-idealistic pursuit to remedy it
has been misguided.

767
01:14:11,041 --> 01:14:14,332
Mary, you have to realise y-you are not
a magic beauty cream

768
01:14:14,375 --> 01:14:18,832
